In the limit , hypermultiplet modes become massless, reflected 
by the appearance of a Higgs branch. In contrast, as , the 
vector multiplet becomes light and a Coulomb branch of vacua appears. 
The parameter  will be defined more precisely below, and plays an important role in 
our story.


